  # ACES — Activation Service Installation

  Notification flow when ACES executes a brand-new FTTH activation:

  Step-01 Accepted
    → Step-02 In-Progress
      → Step-03 Serial-Number-Notification (devices array carrying CPE serial)
        → Step-04 Completed
}
